{"tid":1853062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位請警醒，不要燒村","createTime":"2020-01-30T18:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T02:07:02.000Z","uid":264974,"like":26,"dislike":404,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"0f420b78bf1be5e9e67b44814cd12f1cb1fe703e","tid":1853062,"uid":264974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:02:03.000Z","msg":"看到今晚元朗發生的事，相信大家都十分憤怒。我同大家一樣都好嬲，但係呢個嬲，你會選擇去點樣處理？<br />\n<br />\n過去半年發生過大大小小無數咁多令人髮指嘅事件，無一不令大家心懷憤恨。但係我地係點樣一同經歷面對，直到今日？係憑著理智、智慧、同勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n頭先所發生嘅事，很大可能係敵人默許下發所嘅。佢地咁樣做，唔單只係出於心腸歹毒，更加係想使人以憤怒遮眼，做出唔理智嘅行為。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可以用個人嘅CRITICAL THINKING，去考慮下一步要點做。"},{"pid":"bb1ca8a5eba2371f45fea1251050394b34dd0f28","tid":1853062,"uid":264974,"like":3,"dislike":34,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:03:58.000Z","msg":"對於係連登見到嘅嘢，都希望大家可以獨立思考一下，唔好全單照收。"},{"pid":"f38bbc5dafeffb61ce585a77bc0c6c4eca3136c4","tid":1853062,"uid":16069,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:04:07.000Z","msg":"又想冷靜到d人唔記得？ <br />\n係咪左膠自己諗"},{"pid":"d4ce5854bc9ab23aad2d9ab100fc91c1fe3349ab","tid":1853062,"uid":79793,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:04:28.000Z","msg":"得啦 收皮啦 四眼仔"},{"pid":"fb8113fbf2aa28be4651417d014adfdebfe0c466","tid":1853062,"uid":224929,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:05:32.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，鄉黑死全家呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3620e8685192b6c2db28ed8c0325a6cc1b259cb","tid":1853062,"uid":5929,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"-O-O"},{"pid":"2265d3bf71cfe749647b2b8f7fa4d9dbe35bbc4a","tid":1853062,"uid":21545,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:05:39.000Z","msg":"左膠都嫌你左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac