ile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n燒撚梗村"},{"pid":"b717a8b20aeea03c4d35ebb57d8f6d9d9762ae99","tid":1853062,"uid":12773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:45:14.000Z","msg":"又一件維穩垃圾<br />\n收左幾多錢呀？<br />\n乞兒！"},{"pid":"19cdb1c7d57bea2f2127c82c087023460d8882fc","tid":1853062,"uid":214446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:45:20.000Z","msg":"拉 左膠"},{"pid":"bc1825491c3fe7d1c097aab4cd65a8a633d1bbd1","tid":1853062,"uid":28437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:45:28.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 死膠"},{"pid":"deafe687cfcb025f91ee26f4f1ddd039a3bb9a67","tid":1853062,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:45:35.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割！"},{"pid":"eefff9f269a8c0b5066fa8918bdcf0f8556e4a2b","tid":1853062,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:47:17.000Z","msg":"輸民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700d6df7c2a76f2673223fd43489762399e74971","tid":1853062,"uid":54642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:48:20.000Z","msg":"回你。。。。<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"d9d096988d545f84d3c821b9d71e75b426dfc39a","tid":1853062,"uid":281388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfd12c0b87c2a85e20faa1c66d72a115d8ac0764","tid":1853062,"uid":318362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qDS8bs1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqDS8bs1.png&h=ae604fd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30fa159049b400e320c15d0384168f6b74d02b1","tid":1853062,"uid":258005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep